  ministry `Ministry of Home Affairs`
  department `Department of Border Management`
  longTitle `An Act to provide for the establishment of the Land Ports Authority of India to put in place systems which address security imperatives and for the development and management of facilities for cross border movement of passengers and goods at designated points along the international borders of India and for matters connected therewith or incidental thereto.`
